The following source files contain algorithms and visual design ported from
LiveKit components-js:

  src/audio-analyzer.ts
    Derived from: packages/react/src/hooks/useTrackVolume.ts
    Ported: normalizeDb() function, multiband frequency bin range (100–199),
            and the sqrt normalisation curve from useMultibandTrackVolume.
    Changes: Rewritten as a standalone TypeScript class (AudioAnalyzer) using
             the browser's getUserMedia API directly, with no LiveKit SDK
             dependency. The algorithm itself is unchanged.

  src/audio-visualizer.ts
    Derived from: packages/shadcn/components/agents-ui/agent-audio-visualizer-bar.tsx
    Ported: Visual design concept — pill-shaped bars, proportional sizing
            variants, and frequency-driven height animation.
    Changes: Rewritten as a Lit WebComponent (LitElement) instead of a React
             component. Microphone source, size variants, CSS custom properties,
             and device-switching API are new original work.

